  "instructions": [
    "Saute onion and garlic in sesame oil until translucent.",
    "Add pea pods to the pan and stir-fry for about 5 minutes until they start to brown slightly.",
    "Pour in coconut aminos, lemon juice, nutritional yeast, and optional fish sauce. Stir well.",
    "Season with salt, according to taste.",
    "Toss in bell pepper if using (1 minute), then add snow peas or green beans.",
    "Stir-fry until vegetables are tender but still crisp.",
    "Serve hot."
